  <h1>DevOps Lifecycle</h1>

  <!-- DevOps Lifecycle SVG -->
  <svg width="600" height="600" viewBox="0 0 600 600">
    <circle cx="300" cy="300" r="200" fill="none" stroke="#bdc3c7" stroke-width="3"/>
    <!-- Stages -->
    <g>
      <circle class="stage" cx="300" cy="100" r="40"/>
      <text class="label" x="300" y="105" text-anchor="middle">Plan</text>

      <circle class="stage" cx="430" cy="170" r="40"/>
      <text class="label" x="430" y="175" text-anchor="middle">Develop</text>

      <circle class="stage" cx="500" cy="300" r="40"/>
      <text class="label" x="500" y="305" text-anchor="middle">Build</text>

      <circle class="stage" cx="430" cy="430" r="40"/>
      <text class="label" x="430" y="435" text-anchor="middle">Test</text>

      <circle class="stage" cx="300" cy="500" r="40"/>
      <text class="label" x="300" y="505" text-anchor="middle">Release</text>

      <circle class="stage" cx="170" cy="430" r="40"/>
      <text class="label" x="170" y="435" text-anchor="middle">Deploy</text>

      <circle class="stage" cx="100" cy="300" r="40"/>
      <text class="label" x="100" y="305" text-anchor="middle">Operate</text>

      <circle class="stage" cx="170" cy="170" r="40"/>
      <text class="label" x="170" y="175" text-anchor="middle">Monitor</text>
    </g>
  </svg>

  <!-- Descriptions -->
  <div class="description"><strong>Plan:</strong> Define project requirements, set goals, and outline tasks collaboratively between dev and ops teams.</div>
  <div class="description"><strong>Develop:</strong> Code is written using version control systems and collaboration tools to ensure agility and traceability.</div>
  <div class="description"><strong>Build:</strong> Code is compiled and built automatically using CI/CD pipelines to ensure consistency and speed.</div>
  <div class="description"><strong>Test:</strong> Automated and manual tests are run to catch bugs, ensure quality, and validate functionality early.</div>
  <div class="description"><strong>Release:</strong> Verified builds are prepared for release and tagged as production-ready artifacts.</div>
  <div class="description"><strong>Deploy:</strong> Application is deployed to staging or production environments with automated scripts or container platforms.</div>
  <div class="description"><strong>Operate:</strong> Teams manage and maintain infrastructure, systems, and services to keep the app running smoothly.</div>
  <div class="description"><strong>Monitor:</strong> Logs and metrics are collected and analyzed to detect issues and improve performance and reliability.</div>

